description:
Unua filmo de fama kinoreghisoro Sergej Eisenstein, rakontanta pri laborista lukto en Rusio en la komenco de la dudeka jarcento. Kun subtitoloj en Esperanto. Vd. pli detale che http://kinejo.blogsome.com/2007/08/20/la-striko-1925/

Laborers at a locomotive factory go on strike to protest harsh working conditions. Management rejects their demands and decides to break the strike by any means necessary. (Plot summary from imdb.com).The cinematographic technique of Sergei Eisenstein had been fully demonstrated already in this his first film. Intertitles in Russian and Esperanto. IMDB info - http://imdb.com/title/tt0015361/

